{"type":"message","id":"8712bfcf","parentId":"cf72436b","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:02:40.279Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"所以远程有一个初始提交 \"cb5dd19 Initial commit\"，本地也有一个 \"e191208 Initial commit...\"。它们是两个不同的初始提交，没有共同祖先。\n\n有两种选择：\n1. 从远程拉取那个初始提交，然后我们的提交作为第二个提交（合并历史）\n2. 强制推送（force）覆盖远程的初始提交\n\n由于潘神说\"仓库建好了\"，可能 GitHub 自动生成了一个初始 README 或其他文件。为了保持历史清晰，我应该把远程的初始提交合并进来，然后添加我们的文件作为第二个提交。\n\n让我尝试：先重置本地到远程的提交，然后添加我们的文件并提交，或者使用 git merge 来处理无关历史。\n\n但是更简单的是：既然远程只有一个初始提交（可能只是自动生成的），我可以：\n1. 基于远程创建一个新分支\n2. 添加我们的文件\n3. 提交并推送\n\n让我试试：先 checkout 到远程的 main，然后合并我们的更改。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"我看到远程有一个初始提交（`cb5dd19 Initial commit`）。让我把我们的内容合并进去，而不是覆盖："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_645eb3c78cfc4745b66ec4dc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge- && git checkout -b temp-main origin/main"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8368ca4e88054d4883c4adca","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge- && git merge --allow-unrelated-histories e191208 --message \"Merge VoxBridge project structure (lobster initial setup)\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":70144,"output":659,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70803,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773529353842}}
