{"type":"message","id":"4c731077","parentId":"62849db1","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:15:14.982Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The argostranslate package for en->zh is installed. Now I should:\n\n1. Update .project-info.md to mark dependencies as installed\n2. Create src/ directory with simple stub files (empty for now)\n3. Create test/ directory with basic test scripts\n4. Commit all this to VoxBridge repo\n\nBut wait: The project is already on GitHub. Should I push these changes? Yes, it's part of Day 1 work. Let me add these files and commit.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **argostranslate 语言包已安装（en→zh）**\n\n现在创建源代码和测试目录结构："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7ce064a995124f3ab44b2361","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge- && mkdir -p src tests samples outputs"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2568b031864a4adbb0626107","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nVoxBridge Pipeline - 完整工作流\n\n使用方法：\n    python pipeline.py --input input.mp4 --output output.mp4\n\"\"\"\n\nimport argparse\nimport sys\nimport os\n\n# 添加 src 目录到路径\nsys.path.insert(0, os.path.join(os.path.dirname(__file__), 'src'))\n\ndef main():\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description='English video to Chinese voice translation')\n    parser.add_argument('--input', required=True, help='Input video file (MP4, MKV, etc.)')\n    parser.add_argument('--output', required=True, help='Output video file with Chinese audio')\n    parser.add_argument('--whisper-model', default='base', choices=['tiny', 'base', 'small', 'medium', 'large-v3'],\n                        help='Whisper model size (default: base)')\n    parser.add_argument('--tts-voice', default='zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural', help='Edge-TTS voice name')\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    print(f\"🎬 VoxBridge Pipeline v0.1\")\n    print(f\"   Input: {args.input}\")\n    print(f\"   Output: {args.output}\")\n    print(f\"   Whisper model: {args.whisper_model}\")\n    print(f\"   TTS voice: {args.tts_voice}\")\n\n    # TODO: 实现完整 pipeline\n    print(\"⚠️  Pipeline not implemented yet. Day 2-3 implementation.\")\n    return 0\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    sys.exit(main())\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/pipeline.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9a388b1c7e6a4850930f865b","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nAudio extraction using ffmpeg-python\n\"\"\"\n\nimport ffmpeg\n\ndef extract_audio(video_path, audio_path, sample_rate=16000, channels=1):\n    \"\"\"\n    Extract audio from video to WAV format.\n\n    Args:\n        video_path: Path to input video\n        audio_path: Path to output WAV file\n        sample_rate: Target sample rate (default 16000 for Whisper)\n        channels: Number of audio channels (1 = mono)\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        (\n            ffmpeg\n            .input(video_path)\n            .output(\n                audio_path,\n                acodec='pcm_s16le',\n                ar=str(sample_rate),\n                ac=channels\n            )\n            .run(overwrite_output=True, quiet=True)\n        )\n        return True\n    except ffmpeg.Error as e:\n        print(f\"❌ FFmpeg error: {e.stderr.decode()}\")\n        return False\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # Test extraction\n    extract_audio('../samples/sample.mp4', '../outputs/test.wav')\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/video.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ebbe6d89ec204d0689d44cc8","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nSpeech-to-text using faster-whisper\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom faster_whisper import WhisperModel\n\ndef transcribe(audio_path, model_size='base', language='en', device='cpu', compute_type='int8'):\n    \"\"\"\n    Transcribe audio to text using faster-whisper.\n\n    Args:\n        audio_path: Path to WAV audio file\n        model_size: Whisper model size (tiny, base, small, medium, large-v3)\n        language: Source language code\n        device: 'cpu' or 'cuda'\n        compute_type: For CPU: 'int8' (quantized) for speed/memory savings\n\n    Returns:\n        (text, segments) - full text and segment list with timestamps\n    \"\"\"\n    model = WhisperModel(model_size, device=device, compute_type=compute_type)\n    segments, info = model.transcribe(audio_path, language=language)\n\n    text_parts = []\n    for segment in segments:\n        text_parts.append(segment.text)\n\n    full_text = ' '.join(text_parts)\n    return full_text, segments\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # Quick test\n    text, segs = transcribe('../outputs/test.wav', model_size='tiny')\n    print(f\"Transcribed: {text[:200]}...\")\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/transcribe.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6693efc2bea64ea098b19ec5","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nTranslation using argostranslate (offline)\n\"\"\"\n\nimport argostranslate.package\nimport argostranslate.translate\n\ndef translate_text(text, from_lang='en', to_lang='zh'):\n    \"\"\"\n    Translate text from source language to target language.\n\n    Args:\n        text: Input text string\n        from_lang: Source language code (e.g., 'en')\n        to_lang: Target language code (e.g., 'zh')\n\n    Returns:\n        Translated text string\n    \"\"\"\n    # argostranslate translates via installed packages\n    translated = argostranslate.translate.translate(text, from_lang, to_lang)\n    return translated\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # Quick test\n    result = translate_text(\"Hello, this is a test.\")\n    print(f\"Translated: {result}\")\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/translate.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3c4e7c6600da46eda4ee9a5b","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nText-to-speech using edge-tts (Microsoft Edge online TTS)\n\"\"\"\n\nimport asyncio\nimport edge_tts\n\ndef synthesize_speech(text, output_path, voice='zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural'):\n    \"\"\"\n    Generate Chinese speech from text using edge-tts.\n\n    Args:\n        text: Chinese text to synthesize\n        output_path: Output WAV file path\n        voice: Edge-TTS voice name (default: Chinese female)\n\n    Note: Requires internet connection to Microsoft servers.\n    \"\"\"\n    async def _synthesize():\n        communicate = edge_tts.Communicate(text, voice)\n        await communicate.save(output_path)\n\n    asyncio.run(_synthesize())\n    return os.path.exists(output_path)\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # Quick test\n    synthesize_speech(\"你好，这是一个测试。\", '../outputs/tts_test.wav')\n    print(\"TTS generated: outputs/tts_test.wav\")\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/tts.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_015e3980f85344819cf8a905","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nTest suite for VoxBridge components\n\"\"\"\n\nimport unittest\nimport os\nimport sys\n\n# Add src to path\nsys.path.insert(0, os.path.join(os.path.dirname(__file__), '..', 'src'))\n\nclass TestVideoExtraction(unittest.TestCase):\n    def test_placeholder(self):\n        self.assertTrue(True, \"Placeholder test\")\n\nclass TestTranscribe(unittest.TestCase):\n    def test_placeholder(self):\n        self.assertTrue(True, \"Placeholder test\")\n\nclass TestTranslate(unittest.TestCase):\n    def test_translate_simple(self):\n        from translate import translate_text\n        result = translate_text(\"Hello, world!\", 'en', 'zh')\n        self.assertIsInstance(result, str)\n        self.assertGreater(len(result), 0)\n        print(f\"✅ Translation test: 'Hello, world!' → '{result}'\")\n\nclass TestTTS(unittest.TestCase):\n    def test_placeholder(self):\n        self.assertTrue(True, \"Placeholder test\")\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    print(\"🧪 Running quick component tests...\\n\")\n    # Run specific tests\n    suite = unittest.TestSuite()\n    suite.addTest(TestTranslate('test_translate_simple'))\n    runner = unittest.TextTestRunner(verbosity=2)\n    runner.run(suite)\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/tests/test_components.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fbc3367b0fed4e78a0a03a4c","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# VoxBridge 项目状态更新 (2026-03-15)\n\n## Day 1 完成情况\n\n- [x] GitHub 仓库创建并推送初始结构\n- [x] VM 环境配置（apache benchmark?）不对，是：\n  - [x] apt install python3-venv ffmpeg ✅\n  - [x] 创建虚拟环境 `venv`\n  - [x] pip install -r requirements.txt ✅\n  - [x] argostranslate 语言包安装 (en→zh) ✅\n- [x] 基础源代码结构搭建\n  - [x] src/pipeline.py (骨架)\n  - [x] src/video.py (ffmpeg wrapper)\n  - [x] src/transcribe.py (faster-whisper wrapper)\n  - [x] src/translate.py (argos wrapper)\n  - [x] src/tts.py (edge-tts wrapper)\n  - [x] tests/test_components.py (单元测试骨架)\n- [ ] 实际 pipeline 端到端测试（Day 2-3 任务）\n- [ ] Demo 视频制作（Day 3 任务）\n\n## 环境验证\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| Python 3.12 | ✅ |\n| venv | ✅ |\n| pip install | ✅ (所有依赖已安装) |\n| ffmpeg CLI | ✅ (6.1.1) |\n| faster-whisper | ✅ 1.2.1 |\n| argostranslate | ✅ 1.11.0 (en→zh installed) |\n| edge-tts | ✅ 7.2.7 |\n| ffmpeg-python | ✅ 0.2.0 |\n| torch | ✅ 2.10.0 (CPU only) |\n| torchaudio | ✅ 2.10.0 |\n\n## 下一步\n\n**Day 2 (3月16日):**\n1. 实现各模块完整功能\n2. 编写端到端集成测试\n3. 使用 sample video 测试\n4. 优化参数和错误处理\n\n---\n\n**更新时间：** 2026-03-15 07:30 (Asia/Shanghai)\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/.project-status.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":87844,"output":2624,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90468,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773530096568}}
