{"type":"message","id":"1554c60b","parentId":"324ff4df","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:35:27.738Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1fdb20c5a67c49959c31b0ff","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# VoxBridge - 4天排期计划\n\n**目标：** 3月19日前完成并提交大赛\n\n---\n\n## 📅 Day 1 (3月15日) - 基础设施\n\n- [x] 创建 GitHub 仓库\n- [x] 上传可行性报告和文档\n- [ ] 在 VM 上安装 pip 和 FFmpeg\n- [ ] 克隆仓库到 VM 的 `~/VoxBridge/`（或直接在 workspace 开发）\n- [ ] 测试 pip 环境：安装 faster-whisper、argostranslate 等\n- [ ] 下载 argos 翻译包（en→zh）\n- [ ] 验证各组件能正常 import\n\n**交付物：** 环境就绪，文档上传 GitHub\n\n---\n\n## 📅 Day 2 (3月16日) - Core Pipeline\n\n- [ ] 编写 `src/pipeline.py`（主流程）\n- [ ] 实现 `src/transcribe.py`（封装 faster-whisper）\n- [ ] 实现 `src/translate.py`（封装 argostranslate）\n- [ ] 实现 `src/tts.py`（封装 edge-tts）\n- [ ] 实现 `src/video.py`（封装 ffmpeg-python）\n- [ ] 单元测试 `tests/test_components.py`（各模块独立测试）\n- [ ] 集成测试 `tests/test_pipeline.py`（端到端测试）\n\n**交付物：** pipeline 脚本能完整跑通 test video\n\n---\n\n## 📅 Day 3 (3月17日) - Demo 制作\n\n- [ ] 找 1-2 分钟英文课程视频（清晰音频）\n- [ ] 跑通完整 pipeline，生成中文配音视频\n- [ ] 检查音画同步、语音自然度\n- [ ] 优化参数（Whisper 模型大小、TTS 声音选择）\n- [ ] 添加错误处理（超时重试、fallback 策略）\n- [ ] 如果质量不佳，尝试换 TTS 方案（OpenVoice）\n\n**交付物：** 可播放的 demo 视频（<2分钟）\n\n---\n\n## 📅 Day 4 (3月18日) - 收尾与提交\n\n- [ ] 完善 README.md（项目介绍、安装步骤、使用示例）\n- [ ] 更新 `docs/` 中的技术细节\n- [ ] 制作项目海报（Canva 或 PPT → PDF）\n- [ ] 录制 demo 演示视频（屏幕录制 + 解说）\n- [ ] 打包提交材料（代码、文档、海报、视频）\n- [ ] GitHub Release 创建 v0.1.0 tag\n\n**交付物：** 大赛所需全部材料，GitHub 仓库完整\n\n---\n\n## 📅 Day 5 (3月19日) - 最终检查\n\n- [ ] 检查 GitHub 仓库可克隆、可运行\n- [ ] 测试 README 中的快速启动步骤\n- [ ] 确认无敏感信息（API key 等）\n- [ ] 最终提交大赛平台\n- [ ] 庆祝 🎉\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 风险与缓冲\n\n| 风险 | Day 2 发现 | Day 3 应对 |\n|------|-----------|-----------|\n| Whisper CPU 太慢 | 1分钟音频 >5分钟处理 | 换 tiny 模型，或剪短 demo 长度 |\n| Edge-TTS 网络不稳定 | 请求失败率高 | 添加重试机制，或换 OpenVoice |\n| 内存爆掉 | 转录时 OOM | 关闭其他应用，用 tiny 模型 |\n| 音画不同步 | 有延迟 | 调整 ffmpeg 参数，使用 exact timestamp |\n\n---\n\n**保持灵活，专注可运行的 MVP。** 💪\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773531327730}}
{"type":"message","id":"e54e79a6","parentId":"1554c60b","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:35:40.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Day 1 已完成。现在开始 Day 2 的核心任务：实现完整的 pipeline。\n\n当前代码状况：\n- src/pipeline.py - 骨架，需要完整实现\n- src/video.py - 需要实现 extract_audio 和 merge_audio\n- src/transcribe.py - 需要实现完整转录（包括分段处理）\n- src/translate.py - 需要实现完整翻译（包括分段处理）\n- src/tts.py - 需要实现完整 TTS（包括分段合成和合并）\n- tests/test_components.py - 需要完善\n- tests/test_pipeline.py - 需要创建集成测试\n\n让我开始实现：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我现在全力推进 Day 2，目标是做出能实际运行的 pipeline。\n\n## 🚀 Day 2 任务启动\n\n让我先实现完整的核心模块（目前只是骨架），然后写集成测试。\n\n### 步骤 1: 完善视频处理模块（video.py）"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8f193159165a4990bb6a5d62","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/video.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_87467645b7aa4aac94a737aa","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nVideo processing utilities using ffmpeg-python\n\"\"\"\n\nimport ffmpeg\nimport os\nimport subprocess\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\ndef extract_audio(video_path, audio_path, sample_rate=16000, channels=1):\n    \"\"\"\n    Extract audio from video to WAV format (16kHz mono for Whisper).\n\n    Args:\n        video_path: Path to input video\n        audio_path: Path to output WAV file\n        sample_rate: Target sample rate (default 16000)\n        channels: Number of audio channels (1 = mono)\n\n    Returns:\n        bool: True if successful\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        # Ensure output directory exists\n        os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(audio_path), exist_ok=True)\n\n        (\n            ffmpeg\n            .input(video_path)\n            .output(\n                audio_path,\n                acodec='pcm_s16le',\n                ar=str(sample_rate),\n                ac=channels,\n                loglevel='error'  # Reduce noise\n            )\n            .run(overwrite_output=True)\n        )\n        return True\n    except ffmpeg.Error as e:\n        error_msg = e.stderr.decode() if e.stderr else str(e)\n        print(f\"❌ FFmpeg extraction error: {error_msg}\")\n        return False\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ Unexpected error during audio extraction: {e}\")\n        return False\n\n\ndef replace_audio(video_path, audio_path, output_path, keep_original_audio=False):\n    \"\"\"\n    Replace video audio with new audio file using stream copy (no re-encode).\n\n    Args:\n        video_path: Original video file\n        audio_path: New audio file (WAV/MP3)\n        output_path: Output video file path\n        keep_original_audio: If True, mix original + new; else replace\n\n    Returns:\n        bool: True if successful\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(output_path), exist_ok=True)\n\n        input_video = ffmpeg.input(video_path)\n        input_audio = ffmpeg.input(audio_path)\n\n        if keep_original_audio:\n            # Mix original and new audio (complex filter)\n            # This is simplified; you may need proper audio mixing\n            output = ffmpeg.output(\n                input_video.video,\n                input_audio.audio,\n                output_path,\n                **{'c:v': 'copy', 'c:a': 'aac', 'map': '0:v:0'}\n            )\n        else:\n            # Replace: copy video stream, use new audio\n            output = ffmpeg.output(\n                input_video.video,\n                input_audio.audio,\n                output_path,\n                **{'c:v': 'copy', 'c:a': 'aac', 'map': '0:v:0', 'map': '1:a:0'}\n            )\n\n        output.run(overwrite_output=True, quiet=True)\n        return True\n    except ffmpeg.Error as e:\n        error_msg = e.stderr.decode() if e.stderr else str(e)\n        print(f\"❌ FFmpeg merge error: {error_msg}\")\n        return False\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ Unexpected error during audio replacement: {e}\")\n        return False\n\n\ndef get_video_info(video_path):\n    \"\"\"\n    Get basic video info (duration, resolution, codec) using ffprobe.\n\n    Returns:\n        dict: Video metadata or None if failed\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        probe = ffmpeg.probe(video_path)\n        video_stream = next(s for s in probe['streams'] if s['codec_type'] == 'video')\n        audio_stream = next((s for s in probe['streams'] if s['codec_type'] == 'audio'), None)\n\n        info = {\n            'duration': float(probe['format']['duration']),\n            'size': int(probe['format']['size']),\n            'video_codec': video_stream.get('codec_name'),\n            'width': int(video_stream.get('width', 0)),\n            'height': int(video_stream.get('height', 0)),\n            'audio_codec': audio_stream.get('codec_name') if audio_stream else None,\n        }\n        return info\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ FFmpeg probe error: {e}\")\n        return None\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # Quick manual test (requires sample video)\n    print(\"This module is not meant to be run directly.\")\n    print(\"Use pipeline.py to process videos.\")\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/video.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":100559,"output":1441,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102000,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773531327751}}
{"type":"message","id":"951bbd3b","parentId":"e54e79a6","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:35:40.564Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8f193159165a4990bb6a5d62","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nAudio extraction using ffmpeg-python\n\"\"\"\n\nimport ffmpeg\n\ndef extract_audio(video_path, audio_path, sample_rate=16000, channels=1):\n    \"\"\"\n    Extract audio from video to WAV format.\n\n    Args:\n        video_path: Path to input video\n        audio_path: Path to output WAV file\n        sample_rate: Target sample rate (default 16000 for Whisper)\n        channels: Number of audio channels (1 = mono)\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        (\n            ffmpeg\n            .input(video_path)\n            .output(\n                audio_path,\n                acodec='pcm_s16le',\n                ar=str(sample_rate),\n                ac=channels\n            )\n            .run(overwrite_output=True, quiet=True)\n        )\n        return True\n    except ffmpeg.Error as e:\n        print(f\"❌ FFmpeg error: {e.stderr.decode()}\")\n        return False\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # Test extraction\n    extract_audio('../samples/sample.mp4', '../outputs/test.wav')\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773531340562}}
