{"type":"message","id":"f572dff5","parentId":"40092612","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:48:44.939Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_86dd83d85feb4af99d64abbf","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"============================================================\n🦞 VoxBridge Pipeline v0.1\n============================================================\nInput:  samples/b90e47fa-fbd3-446e-9f8b-ce025e893a56.mp4\nOutput: outputs/b90e47fa-chinese.mp4\nWhisper: tiny\nTTS: zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural\n============================================================\n📹 inspecting video...\n   Duration: 26.4s\n   Resolution: 1280x578\n   Video codec: h264\n\n🔊 Step 1/4: Extracting audio from video...\n   ✅ Audio extracted: 0.8 MB\n\n🗣️  Step 2/4: Transcribing speech to text...\n   Model: faster-whisper-tiny (CPU mode)\n❌ Transcription error: Got: ConnectError: [Errno 101] Network is unreachable\nAn error happened while trying to locate the files on the Hub and we cannot find the appropriate snapshot folder for the specified revision on the local disk. Please check your internet connection and try again.\n❌ Transcription failed or empty\n\n💥 Pipeline failed.\n\nProcess exited with code 1."}],"details":{"status":"failed","sessionId":"faint-dune","exitCode":1,"aggregated":"============================================================\n🦞 VoxBridge Pipeline v0.1\n============================================================\nInput:  samples/b90e47fa-fbd3-446e-9f8b-ce025e893a56.mp4\nOutput: outputs/b90e47fa-chinese.mp4\nWhisper: tiny\nTTS: zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural\n============================================================\n📹 inspecting video...\n   Duration: 26.4s\n   Resolution: 1280x578\n   Video codec: h264\n\n🔊 Step 1/4: Extracting audio from video...\n   ✅ Audio extracted: 0.8 MB\n\n🗣️  Step 2/4: Transcribing speech to text...\n   Model: faster-whisper-tiny (CPU mode)\n❌ Transcription error: Got: ConnectError: [Errno 101] Network is unreachable\nAn error happened while trying to locate the files on the Hub and we cannot find the appropriate snapshot folder for the specified revision on the local disk. Please check your internet connection and try again.\n❌ Transcription failed or empty\n\n💥 Pipeline failed.\n","name":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773532124928}}
