{"type":"message","id":"06b27e17","parentId":"bc4e7624","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:48:59.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"transcribe 模块出错了：faster-whisper-tiny 需要从 Hugging Face Hub 下载模型（首次运行）。但网络不可达（Hugging Face 被墙）。\n\n解决方案：\n1. 手动下载模型到本地（绕过网络）\n2. 或者使用其他方法：直接用离线模型文件\n\n让我检查 faster-whisper 的文档，看看如何指定本地模型路径。实际上，faster-whisper 会自动从 Hugging Face 下载模型到 `~/.cache/`。但这里网络不通。\n\n我可以：\n- 使用 `--model-size` 指定一个本地已存在的模型（如果有）\n- 或者修改代码让 transcribe 接受本地模型路径参数\n- 或者先手动下载模型（需要网络）\n\n更简单的方法：使用 `WhisperModel` 的 `download_root` 参数指定本地目录，然后提前下载模型。但网络不通。\n\n等等，可能有内部镜像？让我检查环境。或者这个 VM 有网络？\n\n从错误看：\"Network is unreachable\" - 说明 Hugging Face 无法访问。\n\n我需要一个不依赖 Hugging Face 的方案：\n1. **OpenAI Whisper（官方的）** - 也需要下载模型\n2. **Vosk** - 离线 ASR，但质量较差\n3. **Coqui STT** - 离线，但安装复杂\n\n或者，我可以修改方案：使用 **在线 ASR API**（如 Azure Speech Services，但需要付费和网络）\n或者，这个比赛允许使用本地模型，我需要解决下载问题。\n\n让我先检查 VM 是否能访问外部网络：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"看到问题了：faster-whisper 首次运行需要从 Hugging Face 下载模型，但网络不通（`Network is unreachable`）。\n\n我需要让模型下载走国内镜像或提前下载。让我修改 transcribe.py 支持本地模型路径，并尝试使用镜像："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c6aa73e942f348bd8a43e05d","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/transcribe.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6900b540afcf40ab8c9f3654","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nSpeech-to-text using faster-whisper with local/cached model support\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom faster_whisper import WhisperModel\nimport os\n\ndef transcribe(audio_path, model_size='base', model_path=None, language='en', device='cpu', compute_type='int8'):\n    \"\"\"\n    Transcribe audio to text using faster-whisper.\n\n    Args:\n        audio_path: Path to WAV audio file\n        model_size: Whisper model size (tiny, base, small, medium, large-v3)\n        model_path: Optional local path to model (overrides model_size)\n        language: Source language code (default 'en')\n        device: 'cpu' or 'cuda' (default 'cpu')\n        compute_type: For CPU: 'int8' (quantized) for speed/memory\n\n    Returns:\n        tuple: (full_text, segments)\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        if model_path:\n            # Use local model directory\n            model = WhisperModel(model_path, device=device, compute_type=compute_type)\n        else:\n            # Use model_size, let faster-whisper handle download/cache\n            model = WhisperModel(model_size, device=device, compute_type=compute_type)\n\n        segments, info = model.transcribe(audio_path, language=language)\n\n        text_parts = []\n        seg_list = []\n\n        for segment in segments:\n            text_parts.append(segment.text)\n            seg_list.append({\n                'start': segment.start,\n                'end': segment.end,\n                'text': segment.text\n            })\n\n        full_text = ' '.join(text_parts).strip()\n        return full_text, seg_list\n\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ Transcription error: {e}\")\n        import traceback\n        traceback.print_exc()\n        return \"\", []\n\n\ndef transcribe_chunks(audio_path, chunk_duration=30, **kwargs):\n    \"\"\"\n    For long audio, split into chunks and transcribe separately.\n    (Not implemented yet - future enhancement)\n    \"\"\"\n    return transcribe(audio_path, **kwargs)\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    test_audio = '../outputs/test.wav'\n    if os.path.exists(test_audio):\n        print(f\"Testing with: {test_audio}\")\n        text, segs = transcribe(test_audio, model_size='tiny')\n        print(f\"Transcription ({len(segs)} segments):\")\n        print(f\"Text: {text[:200]}...\")\n        if segs:\n            print(f\"First segment: start={segs[0]['start']:.2f}, end={segs[0]['end']:.2f}, text='{segs[0]['text'][:50]}...'\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"Test audio not found: {test_audio}\")\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/transcribe.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":115821,"output":1554,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117375,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773532124961}}
{"type":"message","id":"fadaeee2","parentId":"06b27e17","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:48:59.165Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c6aa73e942f348bd8a43e05d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nSpeech-to-text using faster-whisper with segment support\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom faster_whisper import WhisperModel\nimport os\n\ndef transcribe(audio_path, model_size='base', language='en', device='cpu', compute_type='int8'):\n    \"\"\"\n    Transcribe audio to text using faster-whisper.\n\n    Args:\n        audio_path: Path to WAV audio file\n        model_size: 'tiny', 'base', 'small', 'medium', 'large-v3' (default: base)\n        language: Source language code (default: 'en')\n        device: 'cpu' or 'cuda' (default: 'cpu')\n        compute_type: For CPU: 'int8' (quantized) for speed/memory\n\n    Returns:\n        tuple: (full_text, segments)\n            - full_text: str, concatenated transcription\n            - segments: list of segment objects with .text, .start, .end\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        model = WhisperModel(model_size, device=device, compute_type=compute_type)\n        segments, info = model.transcribe(audio_path, language=language)\n\n        text_parts = []\n        seg_list = []\n\n        for segment in segments:\n            text_parts.append(segment.text)\n            seg_list.append({\n                'start': segment.start,\n                'end': segment.end,\n                'text': segment.text\n            })\n\n        full_text = ' '.join(text_parts).strip()\n        return full_text, seg_list\n\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ Transcription error: {e}\")\n        return \"\", []\n\n\ndef transcribe_chunks(audio_path, chunk_duration=30, **kwargs):\n    \"\"\"\n    For long audio, split into chunks and transcribe separately.\n    (Not implemented yet - future enhancement)\n    \"\"\"\n    # Placeholder for future optimization\n    return transcribe(audio_path, **kwargs)\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # Quick standalone test\n    test_audio = '../outputs/test.wav'\n    if os.path.exists(test_audio):\n        text, segs = transcribe(test_audio, model_size='tiny')\n        print(f\"Transcription ({len(segs)} segments):\")\n        print(f\"Text: {text[:200]}...\")\n        print(f\"First segment: {segs[0] if segs else 'none'}\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"Test audio not found: {test_audio}\")\n        print(\"Run pipeline with a real video first.\")\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773532139162}}
