{"type":"message","id":"625409cb","parentId":"280052f5","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:49:06.631Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没改成功，还是旧版本。让我直接检查 pip install 时 faster-whisper 缓存位置，然后手动复制模型文件。但网络不通的情况下，我需要在有网络的环境提前下载模型。\n\n实际上，我有更好的方案：不使用 Hugging Face 自动下载，而是使用本地模型文件。但我们需要先获得模型文件。\n\n我可以：\n1. 通过 wget 从国内镜像下载模型文件到本地\n2. 或者使用 OpenAI 的原始 Whisper（pip install openai-whisper）并指定本地模型\n\n最快的方法是：找一个能下载的国内镜像源。让我检查 Hugging Face 镜像。\n\n我可以设置环境变量 `HF_ENDPOINT` 和 `HF_HUB_DISABLE_TELEMETRY` 来使用镜像。\n\n但环境变量可能在代码中设置更快。让我修改 transcribe.py 在创建模型前设置环境变量。\n\n或者，我直接使用 pip 安装时已经缓存了的模型？但似乎没有。\n\n让我先检查是否有任何 whisper 模型文件在本地：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"问题根源：faster-whisper 需要从 Hugging Face Hub 下载模型，但 VM 网络不可达。我有两个解决方案：\n\n1. **手动下载模型文件**（需要网络）\n2. **改用 OpenAI Whisper（官方的）**——它也可以本地加载模型\n\n让我尝试先下载模型到本地缓存目录："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f27e9dcade9b42f69d56e174","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.cache/ 2>/dev/null | grep -i whisper || echo \"no whisper cache\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3bfa9e13b98241c4a74c19a3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"HF_HUB_DISABLE_TELEMETRY=1 python3 -c \"from huggingface_hub import snapshot_download; snapshot_download(repo_id='Systran/faster-whisper-tiny', local_dir='~/.cache/whisper-tiny')\" 2>&1 | tail -10","timeout":120}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":117489,"output":759,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118248,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773532139208}}
