{"type":"message","id":"e308cf85","parentId":"6c564626","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:49:15.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"huggingface_hub 没有安装。需要下载模型必须用 pip install huggingface_hub。但这又需要网络下载 huggingface_hub。\n\n我有个大胆想法：既然网络不可达，我可以把模型文件从另一个有网络的环境拷贝过来？但我不确定。\n\n或者，我换一个不需要下载的 ASR 引擎：**Vosk** 离线 ASR，模型文件直接下载。但需要安装 vosk，也需要网络。\n\n另一个方案：**使用在线 API 进行转录**（如 Azure, OpenAI Whisper API）——但需要付费和网络。\n\n突然想到：这个 VM 是否可以通过 HTTP 代理上网？或者潘神能提供预先下载好的模型文件？\n\n让我检查环境变量看是否有代理：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"看来需要先下载模型。我换一个更直接的方法：使用 `pip download` 方式提前下载 wheel 和模型，但网络仍然需要。\n\n让我检查 VM 能否访问外网："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a0eac3cc9eb541819b6aba50","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -I https://huggingface.co 2>&1 | head -5"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d4d26d02c696444296808953","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ping -c 2 huggingface.co 2>&1 | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":117982,"output":502,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118484,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773532146741}}
