{"type":"message","id":"5e487355","parentId":"38948164","timestamp":"2026-03-15T00:17:37.244Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! 翻译模块现在工作！ MarianMT 模型下载成功，翻译快速且质量尚可。\n\n现在我需要测试 TTS。edge-tts 需要网络，如果网络不通会失败。让我测试一下：\n\n```bash\nvenv/bin/python3 -c \"import edge_tts; print('edge_tts available')\"  # 仅导入\n```\n\n应该没问题。然后测试实际 TTS：\n\n```bash\nvenv/bin/python3 -c \"import edge_tts; import asyncio; async def test(): await edge_tts.Communicate('你好', 'zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural').save('/tmp/test.wav'); asyncio.run(test())\"\n```\n\n但网络可能不好。让我测试一下网络连通性：\n\nping edge.microsoft.com? 但可能被阻止。\n\n我可以直接尝试 TTS，如果失败就捕获异常。\n\n另外，如果 edge-tts 失败，我可以使用 OpenVoice 作为 fallback，但 OpenVoice 需要下载 checkpoint，同样网络依赖。\n\n另一个选择：使用系统自带的 espeak-ng（已安装？可能有中文语音包？）\n\n让我先测试 edge-tts。如果失败，我会在 code 中添加 fallback 机制。\n\n---\n\n测试 edge-tts 网络连通性。\n\n如果 edge-tts 也网络不通，我只能生成无声视频或跳过 TTS，但这 demo 不完整。\n\n也许我可以**先完成管道**，如果某一步失败就记录错误并继续，生成一个带错误提示的输出。\n\n但用户期待看到完整 demo。\n\n让我测试 edge-tts。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **翻译模块正常！** MarianMT 翻译成功。\n\n现在测试 TTS（edge-tts）——这需要网络连接微软服务器："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_10e508884ee74754b5ce1bec","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge- && venv/bin/python3 << 'EOTEST'\nimport sys, os\nsys.path.append('src')\nimport asyncio\nimport edge_tts\n\ntext = \"你好，这是中文语音测试。\"\noutput = \"outputs/temp/tts_test.wav\"\nos.makedirs(\"outputs/temp\", exist_ok=True)\n\nprint(\"🔊 Testing edge-tts (requires internet to Microsoft)...\")\ntry:\n    async def test_tts():\n        communicate = edge_tts.Communicate(text, \"zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural\")\n        await communicate.save(output)\n    asyncio.run(test_tts())\n    print(f\"✅ TTS success: {output} ({os.path.getsize(output)} bytes)\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"❌ TTS failed: {e}\")\nEOTEST","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":135152,"output":1032,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136184,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773533847248}}
