{"type":"message","id":"1f9c98b9","parentId":"9fd945b5","timestamp":"2026-03-15T00:17:46.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! edge-tts 也工作！网络似乎对边缘TTS服务器是通的（可能是 via CDN）。所以整个 pipeline 已经可以运行了。\n\n现在我已经完成了：\n- 转录 ✅\n- 翻译 ✅ (MarianMT)\n- TTS ✅ (edge-tts)\n- 音频提取 ✅\n\n只剩下最后一步：合并音视频。\n\n让我测试完整 pipeline。但有一个问题：pipeline 使用 `replace_audio` 函数，需要测试。\n\n我就run一次完整 pipeline，但注意处理时间可能较长（26秒视频，转录用了136秒）。为了节省时间，我可以用 `tiny` 模型，已经用了。\n\n让我现在运行完整 pipeline：\n\n```bash\nvenv/bin/python3 src/pipeline.py \\\n  --input samples/b90e47fa-fbd3-446e-9f8b-ce025e893a56.mp4 \\\n  --output outputs/final_demo.mp4 \\\n  --whisper-model tiny \\\n  --tts-voice zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural\n```\n\n但之前 pipeline 会卡住，可能是因为翻译或 TTS 的问题。现在应该通了。\n\n让我运行，并设置超时 600 秒。\n\n等等：pipeline 代码中，翻译后是 `synthesize_segments`，然后 `concat_audio_segments`，然后 `replace_audio`。\n\n我需要确保那个音频合并步骤正确。\n\n让我运行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"🎉 **TTS 也成功！** edge-tts 网络正常。\n\n现在所有模块都工作了！让我运行**完整 pipeline**（这次应该能成功）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6ab9e0dcb1b042f59af49ec8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge- && rm -rf outputs/temp && mkdir -p outputs/temp && venv/bin/python3 src/pipeline.py --input samples/b90e47fa-fbd3-446e-9f8b-ce025e893a56.mp4 --output outputs/final_demo.mp4 --whisper-model tiny --tts-voice zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural 2>&1","timeout":600}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":135793,"output":837,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136630,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773533858718}}
