{"type":"message","id":"69735fab","parentId":"5656de09","timestamp":"2026-03-15T00:22:41.309Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我理解了：\n\n1. **心跳检查**：HEARTBEAT.md 解释了 openclaw 没有后台定时器，真正的定时任务由 Windows 任务计划程序负责。龙虾收到消息被唤醒时才会执行这些任务。\n\n2. **潘神提到的\"🔔 心跳检查完成 - 今日日志状态\"** 可能是他在 Windows 端查看的心跳任务执行状态。\n\n3. **龙虾大赛待办**：潘神问这是什么意思，需要我设置什么。根据 HEARTBEAT.md，这是指 openclaw 的日志同步任务，会在每次对话结束时自动执行（前提是 GitHub 已配置）。我已经配置好了 GitHub 日志推送，所以应该没问题。\n\n4. **round_counter.txt** 当前是 0（在正确的 workspace/memory 路径下）。\n\n现在我需要：\n- 更新 round_counter（每轮对话后加1）\n- 完成 pipeline 的完整运行\n- 向潘神汇报翻译质量和 demo 产出情况\n\n让我先更新 round counter，然后优化 pipeline 参数重新运行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我明白了：\n\n## 🐚 关于心跳展示（HEARTBEAT.md）\n\n这是**openclaw 的任务触发机制**说明：\n- **没有后台定时器**——龙虾只在收到消息时运行\n- **真正的定时任务**由你宿主机的 Windows 任务计划程序（每天 03:00）负责\n- 每次对话结束，我会自动写日志并推 GitHub（已配置好）\n- round_counter 在 `~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/`（沙箱内），现在是 0\n\n**\"龙虾大赛待办\"** 可能是指 GitHub 上的 VoxBridge 项目排期（3月19截止）。我已把排期放在 `docs/plan.md`，不需要额外设置。\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 现在优化并完成 demo 生成\n\n我修改 pipeline，将翻译部分改为 MarianMT（已就绪），然后重新处理你的视频："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3efa3ce5c0654f5eb5d0bbf3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge- && git add -A && git commit -m \"Switch to MarianMT translation + fix for offline environments\" && git push origin main 2>&1 | tail -5"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5e11d31500ba45549b477838","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge- && venv/bin/python3 << 'EOPIPE'\nimport sys, os, time\nsys.path.append('src')\n\n# Import pipeline components\nfrom video import extract_audio, replace_audio, get_video_info\nfrom transcribe import transcribe\nfrom translate import translate_segments\nfrom tts import synthesize_segments\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nBASE = Path.cwd()\noutputs_dir = BASE / 'outputs' / 'demo_final'\ntemp_dir = outputs_dir / 'temp'\nos.makedirs(temp_dir, exist_ok=True)\n\ninput_video = str(BASE / 'samples' / 'b90e47fa-fbd3-446e-9f8b-ce025e893a56.mp4')\noutput_video = str(outputs_dir / 'demo_chinese.mp4')\n\nprint('='*60)\nprint('🦞 VoxBridge Pipeline - FINAL RUN')\nprint('='*60)\nprint(f'Input:  {input_video}')\nprint(f'Output: {output_video}')\nprint('='*60)\n\n# 1. Video info\ninfo = get_video_info(input_video)\nprint(f'📹 Video: {info[\"width\"]}x{info[\"height\"]}, {info[\"duration\"]:.1f}s, {info[\"video_codec\"]}')\n\n# 2. Extract audio\naudio_wav = str(temp_dir / 'orig.wav')\nprint('🔊 Extracting audio...')\nok = extract_audio(input_video, audio_wav)\nif not ok: raise SystemExit(1)\nprint(f'   ✅ Audio: {os.path.getsize(audio_wav)/1024:.0f} KB')\n\n# 3. Transcribe\nprint('🗣️  Transcribing (faster-whisper-tiny)...')\ntext, segs = transcribe(audio_wav, model_size='tiny')\nprint(f'   ✅ {len(segs)} segments, {len(text)} chars')\nprint(f'   Preview: {text[:120]}...')\n\n# 4. Translate\nprint('🌐 Translating (MarianMT)...')\nsegs_zh = translate_segments(segs)\nzh_text = ' '.join(s['text_zh'] for s in segs_zh if s.get('text_zh'))\nprint(f'   ✅ {len(segs_zh)} segments translated')\nprint(f'   Preview: {zh_text[:120]}...')\n\n# 5. TTS\nprint('🔉 Synthesizing speech (edge-tts)...')\nwav_files = synthesize_segments(segs_zh, str(temp_dir / 'wavs'))\nprint(f'   ✅ {len(wav_files)} audio files generated')\n\n# 6. Concatenate WAVs\nprint('🔗 Concatenating audio...')\nconcat_list = temp_dir / 'list.txt'\nwith open(concat_list, 'w') as f:\n    for w in wav_files:\n        f.write(f\"file '{w}'\\n\")\nfinal_audio = str(temp_dir / 'chinese_audio.wav')\nimport subprocess\ncmd = ['ffmpeg', '-f', 'concat', '-safe', '0', '-i', str(concat_list), '-acodec', 'pcm_s16le', '-y', final_audio]\nres = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True)\nif res.returncode != 0:\n    print(f'❌ concat error: {res.stderr}')\n    raise SystemExit(1)\nprint(f'   ✅ Final audio: {os.path.getsize(final_audio)/1024:.0f} KB')\n\n# 7. Merge\nprint('🎬 Muxing video + audio...')\nok = replace_audio(input_video, final_audio, output_video)\nif not ok: raise SystemExit(1)\nprint(f'   ✅ Output: {os.path.getsize(output_video)/1024:.0f} KB')\n\nprint('='*60)\nprint('🎉 Pipeline complete! Demo ready.')\nprint('='*60)\nEOPIPE","timeout":600}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":133427,"output":1716,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135143,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773534146818}}
