{"type":"message","id":"0c7cfd49","parentId":"053aaa7a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T00:31:33.218Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Aha! 翻译模块在下载模型权重。MarianMT 模型虽然已经下载过，但可能是在虚拟环境外？让我检查一下缓存位置。\n\n实际上，我之前是用 `HF_ENDPOINT=https://hf-mirror.com` 环境的，现在 pipeline 里没有设置这个环境变量，导致尝试从 huggingface.co 下载，但是网络不通。\n\n我需要在 translate.py 中设置环境变量，或者在 pipeline 中预先加载模型。让我修改 translate.py 在加载时强制使用 hf-mirror。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"发现问题了！翻译模块尝试从 huggingface.co 下载，但网络不通。我修改 `translate.py`，强制使用 hf-mirror 并缓存模型："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9e25ee778142475586a53a4c","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/translate.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_62a884400d1a44a2b1a2fd55","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nTranslation using MarianMT (Hugging Face transformers) - with hf-mirror support\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nfrom transformers import MarianTokenizer, MarianMTModel\nfrom typing import List\n\n# Set HF mirror to avoid network issues\nos.environ.setdefault('HF_ENDPOINT', 'https://hf-mirror.com')\nos.environ.setdefault('HF_HUB_DISABLE_TELEMETRY', 'true')\n\nMODEL_NAME = \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-mt-en-zh\"\n\n_translator = None\n_tokenizer = None\n\ndef load_model():\n    \"\"\"Lazy load MarianMT model and tokenizer.\"\"\"\n    global _translator, _tokenizer\n    if _translator is None or _tokenizer is None:\n        print(f\"📥 Loading MarianMT model: {MODEL_NAME}\")\n        _tokenizer = MarianTokenizer.from_pretrained(MODEL_NAME)\n        _translator = MarianMTModel.from_pretrained(MODEL_NAME)\n        print(\"✅ Model loaded\")\n    return _tokenizer, _translator\n\ndef translate_text(text: str, from_lang='en', to_lang='zh') -> str:\n    \"\"\"\n    Translate text using MarianMT.\n    \"\"\"\n    if from_lang != 'en' or to_lang != 'zh':\n        return text  # Only support en→zh\n\n    try:\n        tokenizer, model = load_model()\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ Failed to load MarianMT model: {e}\")\n        return text\n\n    try:\n        inputs = tokenizer(text, return_tensors=\"pt\", padding=True, truncation=True, max_length=512)\n        translated = model.generate(**inputs)\n        result = tokenizer.decode(translated[0], skip_special_tokens=True)\n        return result\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ Translation error: {e}\")\n        return text\n\ndef translate_segments(segments: List[dict], from_lang='en', to_lang='zh') -> List[dict]:\n    \"\"\"\n    Translate a list of segment dictionaries.\n    \"\"\"\n    for seg in segments:\n        original = seg['text'].strip()\n        if original:\n            translated = translate_text(original, from_lang, to_lang)\n            seg['text_zh'] = translated\n        else:\n            seg['text_zh'] = ''\n    return segments\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    test = \"Hello world, this is a test.\"\n    result = translate_text(test, 'en', 'zh')\n    print(f\"Translation: '{test}' → '{result}'\")\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/translate.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":135849,"output":954,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136803,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773534681748}}
{"type":"message","id":"5eaab46f","parentId":"0c7cfd49","timestamp":"2026-03-15T00:31:33.267Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9e25ee778142475586a53a4c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nTranslation using MarianMT (Hugging Face transformers) - fully offline if model cached\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom transformers import MarianTokenizer, MarianMTModel\nimport os\nfrom typing import List\n\n# Model name for English to Chinese\nMODEL_NAME = \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-mt-en-zh\"\n\n# Cache directory (same as transformers default)\n# Ensure model is downloaded beforehand or cached\n\n_translator = None\n_tokenizer = None\n\ndef load_model():\n    \"\"\"Lazy load MarianMT model and tokenizer.\"\"\"\n    global _translator, _tokenizer\n    if _translator is None or _tokenizer is None:\n        print(f\"📥 Loading MarianMT model: {MODEL_NAME} (may take a minute)...\")\n        _tokenizer = MarianTokenizer.from_pretrained(MODEL_NAME)\n        _translator = MarianMTModel.from_pretrained(MODEL_NAME)\n        print(\"✅ Model loaded\")\n    return _tokenizer, _translator\n\ndef translate_text(text: str, from_lang='en', to_lang='zh') -> str:\n    \"\"\"\n    Translate text using MarianMT.\n    Falls back to simple character mapping if model not available.\n    \"\"\"\n    if from_lang != 'en' or to_lang != 'zh':\n        print(f\"⚠️  MarianMT only supports en→zh, got {from_lang}→{to_lang}\")\n        return text\n\n    try:\n        tokenizer, model = load_model()\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ Failed to load MarianMT model: {e}\")\n        print(\"   ℹ️  Model needs to be downloaded first (requires internet).\")\n        return text\n\n    try:\n        # Tokenize and translate\n        inputs = tokenizer(text, return_tensors=\"pt\", padding=True, truncation=True, max_length=512)\n        translated = model.generate(**inputs)\n        result = tokenizer.decode(translated[0], skip_special_tokens=True)\n        return result\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ Translation error: {e}\")\n        return text\n\n\ndef translate_segments(segments: List[dict], from_lang='en', to_lang='zh') -> List[dict]:\n    \"\"\"\n    Translate a list of segment dictionaries.\n    \"\"\"\n    for seg in segments:\n        original = seg['text'].strip()\n        if original:\n            translated = translate_text(original, from_lang, to_lang)\n            seg['text_zh'] = translated\n        else:\n            seg['text_zh'] = ''\n    return segments\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # Quick test (will download model if not cached)\n    test = \"Hello world, this is a test.\"\n    result = translate_text(test, 'en', 'zh')\n    print(f\"Translation: '{test}' → '{result}'\")\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773534693263}}
