ated 8 audio segments\n   Concatenating audio segments...\n\n🎬 Step 5/5: Muxing audio with video...\n\n✅ Pipeline complete! Output: outputs/demo_final/chinese.mp4\n⏱️  Total time: 17.0s\n   Output size: 4.7 MB\n\n🎉 Pipeline completed successfully!\n","truncated":false,"exitCode":0},{"sessionId":"faint-river","status":"failed","startedAt":1773534776287,"endedAt":1773534793717,"runtimeMs":17430,"cwd":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace","command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge- && git commit -m \"feat: Switch to MarianMT translation (hf-mirror) + successful 26s demo generation\" && git push origin main","name":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-","tail":"自动在后台执行仓库打包以求最佳性能。\n手工维护参见 \"git help gc\"。\nwarning: 最后一次 gc 操作报告如下信息。请检查原因并删除 .git/gc.log\n在该文件被删除之前，自动清理将不会执行。\n\nwarning: 有太多不可达的松散对象，运行 'git prune' 删除它们。\n\n[main beb556e] feat: Switch to MarianMT translation (hf-mirror) + successful 26s demo generation\n 1 file changed, 8 insertions(+), 15 deletions(-)\n","truncated":false,"exitSignal":"SIGTERM"},{"sessionId":"dawn-claw","status":"failed","startedAt":1773534161326,"endedAt":1773534821998,"runtimeMs":660672,"cwd":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace","command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge- && venv/bin/python3 << 'EOPIPE'\nimport sys, os, time\nsys.path.append('src')\n\n# Import pipeline components\nfrom video import extract_audio, replace_audio, get_video_info\nfrom transcribe import transcribe\nfrom translate import translate_segments\nfrom tts import synthesize_segments\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nBASE = Path.cwd()\noutputs_dir = BASE / 'outputs' / 'demo_final'\ntemp_dir = outputs_dir / 'temp'\nos.makedirs(temp_dir, exist_ok=True)\n\ninput_video = str(BASE / 'samples' / 'b90e47fa-fbd3-446e-9f8b-ce025e893a56.mp4')\noutput_video = str(outputs_dir / 'demo_chinese.mp4')\n\nprint('='*60)\nprint('🦞 VoxBridge Pipeline - FINAL RUN')\nprint('='*60)\nprint(f'Input:  {input_video}')\nprint(f'Output: {output_video}')\nprint('='*60)\n\n# 1. Video info\ninfo = get_video_info(input_video)\nprint(f'📹 Video: {info[\"width\"]}x{info[\"height\"]}, {info[\"duration\"]:.1f}s, {info[\"video_codec\"]}')\n\n# 2. Extract audio\naudio_wav = str(temp_dir / 'orig.wav')\nprint('🔊 Extracting audio...')\nok = extract_audio(input_video, audio_wav)\nif not ok: raise SystemExit(1)\nprint(f'   ✅ Audio: {os.path.getsize(audio_wav)/1024:.0f} KB')\n\n# 3. Transcribe\nprint('🗣️  Transcribing (faster-whisper-tiny)...')\ntext, segs = transcribe(audio_wav, model_size='tiny')\nprint(f'   ✅ {len(segs)} segments, {len(text)} chars')\nprint(f'   Preview: {text[:120]}...')\n\n# 4. Translate\nprint('🌐 Translating (MarianMT)...')\nsegs_zh = translate_segments(segs)\nzh_text = ' '.join(s['text_zh'] for s in segs_zh if s.get('text_zh'))\nprint(f'   ✅ {len(segs_zh)} segments translated')\nprint(f'   Preview: {zh_text[:120]}...')\n\n# 5. TTS\nprint('🔉 Synthesizing speech (edge-tts)...')\nwav_files = synthesize_segments(segs_zh, str(temp_dir / 'wavs'))\nprint(f'   ✅ {len(wav_files)} audio files generated')\n\n# 6. Concatenate WAVs\nprint('🔗 Concatenating audio...')\nconcat_list = temp_dir / 'list.txt'\nwith open(concat_list, 'w') as f:\n    for w in wav_files:\n        f.write(f\"file '{w}'\\n\")\nfinal_audio = str(temp_dir / 'chinese_audio.wav')\nimport subprocess\ncmd = ['ffmpeg', '-f', 'concat', '-safe', '0', '-i', str(concat_list), '-acodec', 'pcm_s16le', '-y', final_audio]\nres = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True)\nif res.returncode != 0:\n    print(f'❌ concat error: {res.stderr}')\n    raise SystemExit(1)\nprint(f'   ✅ Final audio: {os.path.getsize(final_audio)/1024:.0f} KB')\n\n# 7. Merge\nprint('🎬 Muxing video + audio...')\nok = replace_audio(input_video, final_audio, output_video)\nif not ok: raise SystemExit(1)\nprint(f'   ✅ Output: {os.path.getsize(output_video)/1024:.0f} KB')\n\nprint('='*60)\nprint('🎉 Pipeline complete! Demo ready.')\nprint('='*60)\nEOPIPE","name":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-","tail":"'[Errno 101] Network is u