{"type":"message","id":"850544d2","parentId":"7031b75f","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:05:22.567Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"web_search 需要 API key，我现在无法使用。但我知道 yt-dlp 是 YouTube 下载的主流工具，稳定可靠。我可以直接基于 yt-dlp 写一个简单的下载器模块。\n\n### 我的建议：\n1. **短期（今天 Day 3）**：使用 yt-dlp 命令直接下载测试视频，手动执行\n2. **中期（Day 4 或之后）**：将 yt-dlp 集成到 VoxBridge 作为可选 `--download` 功能，但不强制依赖（避免无法离线运行）\n3. **长期**：考虑支持本地视频 + 在线视频两种模式\n\n现在，我继续完善 pipeline 的 error handling 和重试机制。让我补充完整 pipeline.py 的修改。\n\n### 需要修改 pipeline.py 的地方：\n1. 加载术语表（在 process_video 开头）\n2. 添加磁盘空间检查\n3. 为 edge-tts 添加重试（失败时重试 3 次）\n4. 更好的错误恢复（例如 transcription 失败时用 base 模型重试？）\n\n让我快速完成这些修改。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Web 搜索不可用。但我基于已知信息：\n\n**yt-dlp** 是 YouTube 下载的王者（fork 自 youtube-dl，star 数极高，持续维护）。  \n**scrapling** 可能更通用，但 yt-dlp 在视频领域更专业。\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 我的建议\n\n**Day 3 优先：** 先用 yt-dlp 快速获取测试视频，验证长视频稳定性。\n\n**可选扩展：** 后续可研究 scrapling 作为通用抓取技能（用于其他项目）。\n\n我将创建视频下载模块："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_775badc927dd41c69fbc7769","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nVideo downloader using yt-dlp\n\"\"\"\n\nimport subprocess\nimport os\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\ndef download_youtube_video(\n    url: str,\n    output_dir: str,\n    max_duration_sec: int = 120,  # 最长 2 分钟\n    max_filesize_mb: int = 50\n) -> str:\n    \"\"\"\n    Download a YouTube video using yt-dlp.\n\n    Args:\n        url: YouTube URL\n        output_dir: Directory to save video\n        max_duration_sec: Maximum video duration (seconds)\n        max_filesize_mb: Maximum file size (MB)\n\n    Returns:\n        Path to downloaded video file, or empty string if failed\n    \"\"\"\n    output_template = os.path.join(output_dir, '%(title)s.%(ext)s')\n\n    cmd = [\n        sys.executable, '-m', 'yt_dlp',\n        '-f', 'best[height<=720]',  # 720p 或更低\n        '--max-filesize', f'{max_filesize_mb}M',\n        '--max-downloads', '1',\n        '--no-playlist',\n        '--output', output_template,\n        '--quiet',\n        '--no-warnings',\n        url\n    ]\n\n    # 如果需要限制时长，添加 duration 过滤（yt-dlp 不支持直接过滤，需后续检查）\n\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=60)\n        if result.returncode != 0:\n            print(f\"❌ yt-dlp failed: {result.stderr}\")\n            return \"\"\n\n        # yt-dlp 会输出下载的文件名到 stdout（在 quiet 模式下可能没有）\n        # 我们直接查找输出目录中最新的视频文件\n        output_path = Path(output_dir)\n        video_files = list(output_path.glob('*.mp4')) + list(output_path.glob('*.webm')) + list(output_path.glob('*.mkv'))\n        if not video_files:\n            print(\"❌ No video file downloaded\")\n            return \"\"\n\n        latest = max(video_files, key=lambda p: p.stat().st_mtime)\n        print(f\"✅ Downloaded: {latest.name}\")\n\n        # 检查时长（可选，需要 ffprobe）\n        # 这里先返回路径\n        return str(latest)\n\n    except subprocess.TimeoutExpired:\n        print(\"❌ yt-dlp timeout\")\n        return \"\"\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ Download error: {e}\")\n        return \"\"\n\n\ndef download_from_url(url: str, output_path: str) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"\n    Simple wrapper: download to specific output path.\n\n    Returns:\n        bool: True if success\n    \"\"\"\n    output_dir = os.path.dirname(output_path)\n    os.makedirs(output_dir, exist_ok=True)\n\n    downloaded = download_youtube_video(url, output_dir)\n    if downloaded:\n        # Rename to desired output path if needed\n        if downloaded != output_path:\n            os.rename(downloaded, output_path)\n        return True\n    return False\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # Quick test (requires yt-dlp installed)\n    if len(sys.argv) > 1:\n        test_url = sys.argv[1]\n        out_dir = 'samples'\n        os.makedirs(out_dir, exist_ok=True)\n        path = download_youtube_video(test_url, out_dir)\n        print(f\"Downloaded to: {path}\" if path else \"Download failed\")\n    else:\n        print(\"Usage: python downloader.py <youtube_url>\")\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/downloader.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":182749,"output":1502,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":184251,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773536709833}}
