{"type":"message","id":"b7d40571","parentId":"db6c81aa","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:22:50.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，现在继续添加 TTS 重试。我需要在 synthesize_segments 调用处包裹 retry 装饰器，因为 edge-tts 可能网络不稳定。\n\n但 pipeline.py 中的 synthesize_segments 是调用 tts.py 的函数。我可以在 tts.py 内部添加重试，或者在这里处理。\n\n更简单：在 tts.py 的 synthesize_speech 里添加 retry。\n\n让我修改 tts.py 为：\n- 使用 utils.retry 装饰器包裹 synthesize_speech\n- 或者添加内部重试逻辑\n\n让我先更新 tts.py。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"现在更新 `tts.py` 添加重试机制："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e2e96fa9730d433b9ac59e37","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge-/src/tts.py","newText":"\"\"\"\nText-to-speech using edge-tts (Microsoft Edge online service)\n\"\"\"\n\nimport asyncio\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport time\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# Add src to path for utils\nBASE_DIR = Path(__file__).parent.absolute()\nsys.path.insert(0, str(BASE_DIR / 'src'))\nfrom utils import retry\n\nimport edge_tts\nfrom typing import List\n\n@retry(max_attempts=3, delay=2.0, backoff=1.5, exceptions=(Exception,))\ndef synthesize_speech(text: str, output_path: str, voice: str = 'zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural') -> bool:\n    \"\"\"\n    Generate Chinese speech from text using edge-tts with retry.\n\n    Args:\n        text: Chinese text to synthesize (max 5000 chars recommended)\n        output_path: Output WAV file path\n        voice: Edge-TTS voice name (default: Chinese female)\n\n    Returns:\n        bool: True if successful\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(output_path), exist_ok=True)\n\n        async def _synthesize():\n            communicate = edge_tts.Communicate(text, voice)\n            await communicate.save(output_path)\n\n        # Run async function in event loop\n        asyncio.run(_synthesize())\n\n        # Verify output file exists and has size\n        if os.path.exists(output_path) and os.path.getsize(output_path) > 1000:\n            return True\n        else:\n            print(f\"❌ TTS output invalid: {output_path}\")\n            return False\n\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ TTS error: {e}\")\n        raise  # Let retry handle it","oldText":"\"\"\"\nText-to-speech using edge-tts (Microsoft Edge online service)\n\"\"\"\n\nimport asyncio\nimport os\nimport edge_tts\nfrom typing import List\n\ndef synthesize_speech(text: str, output_path: str, voice: str = 'zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural') -> bool:\n    \"\"\"\n    Generate Chinese speech from text using edge-tts.\n\n    Args:\n        text: Chinese text to synthesize (max 5000 chars recommended)\n        output_path: Output WAV file path\n        voice: Edge-TTS voice name (default: Chinese female)\n\n    Returns:\n        bool: True if successful\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(output_path), exist_ok=True)\n\n        async def _synthesize():\n            communicate = edge_tts.Communicate(text, voice)\n            await communicate.save(output_path)\n\n        # Run async function in event loop\n        asyncio.run(_synthesize())\n\n        # Verify output file exists and has size\n        if os.path.exists(output_path) and os.path.getsize(output_path) > 1000:\n            return True\n        else:\n            print(f\"❌ TTS output invalid: {output_path}\")\n            return False\n\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ TTS error: {e}\")\n        return False"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":45370,"output":1011,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46381,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773537762179}}
