{"type":"message","id":"a0ab01c4","parentId":"379d3a00","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:24:21.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文件不存在，我需要创建并写入内容。现在我将组织重要的记忆信息，包括：\n\n1. VoxBridge Day 3 的进展\n2. 创建的技能（scrapling）\n3. 路线图目标\n4. 关键技术决策\n5. 需要用户提供的资源\n6. 提醒事项\n\n让我准备一个全面的条目。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ab609dbb9db64bdd82bd4d1e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# VoxBridge Day 3 Memory (2026-03-15)\n\n## 今日完成\n\n### Core Improvements\n- ✅ Error handling framework (`utils.py`): retry decorator, disk checks, ensure_dir\n- ✅ Translation quality boost (`translate.py`): glossary support with 50+ CS terms\n- ✅ TTS reliability (`tts.py`): 3-attempt retry with exponential backoff\n- ✅ Scrapling skill documented (`skills/scrapling/SKILL.md`)\n- ✅ Roadmap with long-term goals (`docs/roadmap.md`):\n  - Accurate terminology\n  - Audio-video sync\n  - Natural speech (emotional, non-mechanical)\n  - Tone/style mimicry\n  - NotebookLM integration\n\n### Dependencies Installed\n- `scrapling==0.4.2`\n- `yt-dlp` (but network unstable, downloads fail)\n\n### Demo Status\n- Day 2 demo: `outputs/demo_final/chinese.mp4` (26s, 4.8 MB) - ✅ Success\n- Day 3 long video test: pending (need 1-2 min CS video input)\n\n### Git Issues\n- `.git/index.lock` persistent conflicts from aggressive gc\n- docs updated but push blocked; manual intervention needed later\n\n### Resource Needs\n- User to provide 1-2 minute English CS course video\n- Confirm TTS optimization direction (multi-voice, SSML prosody)\n\n## Decisions\n- Keep CPU-only models (faster-whisper-tiny/base) for 4GB RAM constraint\n- Pre-download all models using hf-mirror for offline runtime\n- Use `edge-tts` as primary TTS (online but reliable)\n- Abandon `argostranslate` due to `stanza` network dependency\n- Glossary preprocessing: uppercase terms to guide MarianMT\n- Retry strategy: exponential backoff, 3 attempts\n\n## Open TODOs\n- [ ] Test with long video (>=1min) using `--whisper-model tiny`\n- [ ] Explore edge-tts voices (YunxiNeural, XiaoyiNeural) for emotional range\n- [ ] Add SSML controls (rate, pitch, contour) to `tts.py`\n- [ ] Resolve git lock and push `docs/plan.md`, `docs/roadmap.md`\n- [ ] Implement real-time progress bar (tqdm) in pipeline\n- [ ] Audio duration matching (adjust TTS speed to match original segments)\n- [ ] NotebookLM integration design (course framework → translation guidance)\n\n## Key Files\n- `src/pipeline.py` - integrated error handling, glossary load, disk checks\n- `src/utils.py` - new utility module\n- `src/translate.py` - glossary support added\n- `src/tts.py` - retry added\n- `src/downloader.py` - yt-dlp wrapper (experimental)\n- `docs/roadmap.md` - long-term vision\n- `docs/day3-plan.md` - Day 3 task list\n- `docs/day3-progress.md` - progress summary\n- `skills/scrapling/SKILL.md` - scrapper skill spec\n- `glossary.txt` - terminology mapping (50+ CS terms)\n- `requirements.txt` - needs update: add `scrapling`, `yt-dlp`\n\n## User Requests\n- \"准确翻译专业名词\" → glossary system implemented\n- \"音画同步\" → need to align TTS duration with original segment timing\n- \"语序正确\" → MarianMT baseline, glossary helps\n- \"人情味输出，模仿语音语气语调\" → multi-voice + SSML planned\n- \"NotebookLM配合\" → future integration (course outline → translation context)\n\n## Metrics\n- Day 2 demo: 26s video → ~17min total processing (CPU)\n- Models cached: faster-whisper-tiny, opus-mt-en-zh\n- Virtual env: `venv/`\n- Memory: ~4GB limit, swap available\n\n## Reminders\n- Do NOT push large output files to git (add to .gitignore)\n- Always use `venv/bin/python3`\n- Scan for secrets before any git push (L0.3)\n- Round counter: currently 0 (next update at session end)\n- Heartbeat: external Windows task handles rule sync\n","file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-15.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":48223,"output":1159,"cacheRead