angNeural）\n   - 添加 SSML 控制（语速、语调、停顿）\n   - 还是先测试长视频稳定性？\n\n我将在您推送完成后继续开发。🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":132179,"output":790,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132969,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773538272576}}
