{"type":"message","id":"0b57260b","parentId":"2fe0d8ad","timestamp":"2026-03-15T05:38:11.476Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3d2a9a83930343f68646144b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nSpeech-to-text using faster-whisper with local/cached model support\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom faster_whisper import WhisperModel\nimport os\n\ndef transcribe(audio_path, model_size='base', model_path=None, language='en', device='cpu', compute_type='int8'):\n    \"\"\"\n    Transcribe audio to text using faster-whisper.\n\n    Args:\n        audio_path: Path to WAV audio file\n        model_size: Whisper model size (tiny, base, small, medium, large-v3)\n        model_path: Optional local path to model (overrides model_size)\n        language: Source language code (default 'en')\n        device: 'cpu' or 'cuda' (default 'cpu')\n        compute_type: For CPU: 'int8' (quantized) for speed/memory\n\n    Returns:\n        tuple: (full_text, segments)\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        if model_path:\n            # Use local model directory\n            model = WhisperModel(model_path, device=device, compute_type=compute_type)\n        else:\n            # Use model_size, let faster-whisper handle download/cache\n            model = WhisperModel(model_size, device=device, compute_type=compute_type)\n\n        segments, info = model.transcribe(audio_path, language=language)\n\n        text_parts = []\n        seg_list = []\n\n        for segment in segments:\n            text_parts.append(segment.text)\n            seg_list.append({\n                'start': segment.start,\n                'end': segment.end,\n\n[33 more lines in file. Use offset=41 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773553091472}}
{"type":"message","id":"9e8d7026","parentId":"0b57260b","timestamp":"2026-03-15T05:38:11.480Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_746d6f071a824eb78bbcf1c0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nTranslation using MarianMT (Hugging Face transformers) - with glossary support\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nfrom transformers import MarianTokenizer, MarianMTModel\nfrom typing import List, Dict\n\n# Set HF mirror to avoid network issues\nos.environ.setdefault('HF_ENDPOINT', 'https://hf-mirror.com')\nos.environ.setdefault('HF_HUB_DISABLE_TELEMETRY', 'true')\n\nMODEL_NAME = \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-mt-en-zh\"\n\n_translator = None\n_tokenizer = None\n\n# Glossary (term mapping) - can be loaded from external file\nGLOSSARY = {\n    # 示例术语，实际应从文件加载\n    # \"digital brains\": \"数字大脑\",\n    # \"AI\": \"人工智能\",\n    # \"machine learning\": \"机器学习\",\n}\n\n\ndef load_glossary(glossary_path: str = None) -> Dict[str, str]:\n    \"\"\"\n    Load glossary from a file (tab-separated: en\\tzh).\n\n\n[125 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773553091476}}
{"type":"message","id":"b7b97543","parentId":"9e8d7026","timestamp":"2026-03-15T05:38:11.488Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_26d52175fc5f4d80af3d7079","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nText-to-speech using edge-tts (Microsoft Edge online service)\n\"\"\"\n\nimport asyncio\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport time\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# Add src to path for utils\nBASE_DIR = Path(__file__).parent.absolute()\nsys.path.insert(0, str(BASE_DIR / 'src'))\nfrom utils import retry\n\nimport edge_tts\nfrom typing import List\n\n@retry(max_attempts=3, delay=2.0, backoff=1.5, exceptions=(Exception,))\ndef synthesize_speech(text: str, output_path: str, voice: str = 'zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural') -> bool:\n    \"\"\"\n    Generate Chinese speech from text using edge-tts with retry.\n\n    Args:\n        text: Chinese text to synthesize (max 5000 chars recommended)\n        output_path: Output WAV file path\n        voice: Edge-TTS voice name (default: Chinese female)\n\n    Returns:\n        bool: True if successful\n\n[78 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773553091480}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc59f1fa","parentId":"b7b97543","timestamp":"2026-03-15T05:38:20.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我找到了：\n\n1. **转录模型**：faster-whisper\n   - 默认 model_size: 'base'（可在命令行覆盖）\n   - 设备: 'cpu'\n   - 计算类型: 'int8'（量化，节约内存）\n   - 支持 model_path 本地模型路径\n\n2. **翻译模型**：MarianMT\n   - 模型名: \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-mt-en-zh\"\n   - 从hf-mirror下载（避免外网）\n   - 已集成术语表支持\n\n3. **TTS**：edge-tts\n   - 默认音色: 'zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural'（微软晓晓）\n   - 已添加重试机制（3次，指数退避）\n\n让我给潘神一个清晰的模型配置总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🤖 VoxBridge 当前模型配置\n\n### 1. **语音转录 (STT)**\n- **引擎**: `faster-whisper`\n- **默认模型**: `base`（可在命令行覆盖为 `tiny`/`small`/`medium`）\n- **设备**: `cpu`\n- **量化**: `int8`（节省内存，适合 4GB 环境）\n- **预下载模型**: `~/.cache/huggingface/models--Systran--faster-whisper-base`（通过 hf-mirror）\n\n---\n\n### 2. **翻译 (MT)**\n- **引擎**: `MarianMT` (Helsinki-NLP)\n- **模型**: `Helsinki-NLP/opus-mt-en-zh`\n- **预处理**: 术语表支持（glossary.txt，50+ CS 术语）\n- **环境**: `HF_ENDPOINT=https://hf-mirror.com`（离线运行）\n\n---\n\n### 3. **语音合成 (TTS)**\n- **引擎**: `edge-tts` (Microsoft Edge 在线服务)\n- **默认音色**: `zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural`（晓晓，女声）\n- **重试**: 3次指数退避（网络超时自动重试）\n- **备注**: 需联网调用微软 API（实测通畅）\n\n---\n\n### 4. **视频处理**\n- **引擎**: `ffmpeg` (系统安装)\n- **操作**: 音频提取、音频替换（stream copy）\n\n---\n\n## 📊 完整技术栈\n\n| 模块 | 工具 | 模型/参数 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| 转录 | faster-whisper | base (int8, CPU) |\n| 翻译 | transformers (MarianMT) | opus-mt-en-zh |\n| TTS | edge-tts | zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural |\n| 视频 | ffmpeg-python | stream copy |\n\n---\n\n**是否要调整模型配置？** 例如：\n- 转录用 `tiny`（更快，内存更少）\n- TTS 尝试其他音色（XiaoyiNeural/YunxiNeural）\n\n告诉我你的偏好！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":147377,"output":855,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148232,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773553091489}}
