{"type":"message","id":"4c95ef0a","parentId":"3459c31f","timestamp":"2026-03-15T08:39:48.129Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if there's a way for them to test/use the VoxBridge tool. Let me think about options:\n\n1. **Web UI** - Build a simple Gradio/Streamlit interface that they can access via browser\n2. **CLI** - They could SSH into the VM and run commands\n3. **Feishu Bot** - They could send video files via Feishu and get results back\n4. **Expose via Tailscale** - The VM already has Tailscale HTTPS access\n\nThe most practical options:\n- **Gradio Web UI** - Quick to build, accessible via Tailscale URL\n- **Feishu Bot Integration** - Send video, get back translated video\n\n\n- \nGiven they're already using Feishu to communicate with me, a Gradio interface exposed through Tailscale seems like the fastest path—they could access it directly in their browser without leaving their current workflow.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"有几个方案，从简单到复杂：\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 方案对比\n\n| 方案 | 难度 | 体验 | 时间 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| **A. Gradio Web UI** | ⭐⭐ | 浏览器上传视频 → 下载结果 | ~30分钟 |\n| **B. 飞书直传** | ⭐⭐⭐ | 发视频给我 → 自动处理 → 回传 | ~1小时 |\n| **C. SSH 命令行** | ⭐ | 你自己跑脚本 | 即时 |\n| **D. Tailscale 共享链接** | ⭐⭐ | 分享 Web UI 给别人用 | +Gradio |\n\n---\n\n## 推荐：Gradio Web UI（最快落地）\n\n我搭一个简单的 Web 界面，通过 Tailscale 暴露，你直接浏览器访问：\n\n```\nhttps://xzy0626-vmware-virtual-platform.tail6f9a39.ts.net:7860\n```\n\n**功能：**\n- 上传英文视频（mp4/mov）\n- 选择 Whisper 模型（tiny/base）\n- 选择 TTS 音色\n- 点击\"开始处理\"\n- 下载中文配音视频\n\n---\n\n**你想用哪种方式？** 我现在就可以开始搭 Gradio UI。🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":760,"output":701,"cacheRead":195264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":196725,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773563963449}}
