{"type":"message","id":"738091d5","parentId":"8bd3367a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T08:49:53.495Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The firewall is blocking port 7860. Only ports 22 (SSH) and 18789 (OpenClaw) are allowed. I need to add port 7860 to the firewall rules.But the user said they don't want to expose this to the public internet. Since UFW is active, I need to add a rule to allow port 7860 from the local network (192.168.1.0/24).Let me inform the user and ask for permission to add the firewall rule.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"找到原因了！**防火墙 UFW 阻止了 7860 端口**。\n\n当前只开放了：\n- `22/tcp` - SSH\n- `18789/tcp` - OpenClaw（仅局域网）\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 解决方案\n\n需要添加一条防火墙规则（只允许局域网访问）：\n\n```bash\nsudo ufw allow from 192.168.1.0/24 to any port 7860 comment \"VoxBridge-WebUI-LAN-only\"\n```\n\n**这会：**\n- ✅ 只允许局域网 `192.168.x.x` 访问\n- ✅ 不暴露公网\n- ✅ 与 OpenClaw 的 18789 规则一致\n\n**你可以在 VM 终端手动执行，或者授权我执行。**\n\n要我帮你加上吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":426,"output":426,"cacheRead":201984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":202836,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773564579664}}
