{"type":"message","id":"5baa4ca6","parentId":"a554131f","timestamp":"2026-03-15T08:54:19.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Gradio server is still running. The user might not have clicked the \"Start Processing\" button yet, or it's still processing. Let me wait for the user's response about whether they clicked the button or not.Also, I should note that the Gradio UI will spawn a new pipeline process when the user clicks the button, but that process will be separate from the ones we've been running. The output should go to `outputs/webui/`.If the user did click the button and nothing happened, it might be because:1. The pipeline failed silently2. The output file wasn't saved correctly3. There was a permission issueLet me just wait for the user's response.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Gradio 服务器还在运行（pid 28471）。\n\n**你点击\"开始处理\"了吗？**\n\n- **还没点** → 点击后等待处理完成，输出会出现在 `outputs/webui/`\n- **点了但没反应** → 我来检查日志排查问题\n- **点了报错了** → 把错误信息发给我\n\n---\n\n另外，处理进度会在 Web UI 的状态栏显示，你可以看到当前在执行哪一步（转录/翻译/TTS/合成）。\n\n告诉我你看到的情况！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":329,"output":423,"cacheRead":204608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":205360,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773564847260}}
{"type":"message","id":"71eb9493","parentId":"5baa4ca6","timestamp":"2026-03-15T08:57:11.053Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Queued messages while agent was busy]\n\n---\nQueued #1\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54530cd828a4b2890af8d055b4c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_5bbcd0b72f9761f0e23d8396b5ca91e1\",\n  \"sender\": \"潘神\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-15 16:56 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"潘神 (ou_5bbcd0b72f9761f0e23d8396b5ca91e1)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_5bbcd0b72f9761f0e23d8396b5ca91e1\",\n  \"name\": \"潘神\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54530cd828a4b2890af8d055b4c]\n潘神: 我点了开始处理之后，他显示开始处理，然后现在进度条卡在了10.0%但是右下角的秒数一直在增加"}],"timestamp":1773565031045}}
{"type":"message","id":"565daa1f","parentId":"71eb9493","timestamp":"2026-03-15T08:58:10.530Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that after clicking \"Start Processing\", the progress bar is stuck at 10% but the timer in the bottom right keeps increasing. This means the pipeline is running but the progress bar isn't updating properly.\n\nThe issue is likely that:\n1. The pipeline is running but Gradio's progress callback isn't being updated properly\n2. The progress bar is only set to 10% at the start and never updated during processing\n\nLet me check the Gradio app code - I only set `progress(0.1, desc=\"开始处理...\")` at the beginning and never updated it during the pipeline execution.\n\nThe fix would be to:\n1. Add progress callbacks throughout the pipeline\n\n\n2. Or run the pipeline in a way that updates progress\n\nBut that would require modifying the pipeline code to accept a progress callback. A simpler approach is to use Gradio's built-in progress tracking with the `gr.Progress()` object and update it at each step. Since `process_video` in pipeline.py runs as a single blocking call, I should check if it has any progress callback support, and if not, I'll need to modify it to report progress back to Gradio.\n\nLooking at the pipeline code, it just runs through all steps sequentially without any progress reporting. The progress bar is stuck at 10% because that's the only update I'm making. For a long-running task like this, I need to pass the progress callback into the pipeline and have it update at each stage—extracting audio, transcribing, translating, and synthesizing. The quickest fix would be wrapping the pipeline execution and manually updating progress at each step, but that won't work since the pipeline is blocking and doesn't report intermediate progress.\n\nThe better approach is to modify the pipeline function to accept an optional progress callback, then have each major step report its own progress. That way the UI can show meaningful updates as the work progresses.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"进度条卡在 10% 是因为代码只在开始时更新了一次，中间步骤没有更新进度。这是 UI bug，**不影响实际处理**——它在后台正常运行，只是进度条没动。\n\n让我修复进度显示："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"2dbca24c-ab15-48de-b300-9363fc4fae85","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge/app.py","old_string":"def process_video_gradio(\n    video_file,\n    whisper_model,\n    tts_voice,\n    progress=gr.Progress()\n):\n    \"\"\"\n    Process video through VoxBridge pipeline.\n    \"\"\"\n    if video_file is None:\n        return None, \"❌ 请先上传视频文件\"\n\n    # Create output path\n    input_name = Path(video_file).stem\n    output_path = str(OUTPUT_DIR / f\"{input_name}_chinese.mp4\")\n\n    progress(0.1, desc=\"开始处理...\")\n\n    try:\n        # Run pipeline\n        success = process_video(\n            input_path=video_file,\n            output_path=output_path,\n            whisper_model=whisper_model,\n            tts_voice=tts_voice\n        )\n\n        if success and os.path.exists(output_path):\n            file_size = os.path.getsize(output_path) / 1024 / 1024\n            return output_path, f\"✅ 处理完成！\\n输出文件: {Path(output_path).name}\\n大小: {file_size:.1f} MB\"\n        else:\n            return None, \"❌ 处理失败，请检查日志\"\n\n    except Exception as e:\n        return None, f\"❌ 错误: {str(e)}\"","new_string":"def process_video_gradio(\n    video_file,\n    whisper_model,\n    tts_voice,\n    progress=gr.Progress()\n):\n    \"\"\"\n    Process video through VoxBridge pipeline with progress tracking.\n    \"\"\"\n    if video_file is None:\n        return None, \"❌ 请先上传视频文件\"\n\n    # Create output path\n    input_name = Path(video_file).stem\n    output_path = str(OUTPUT_DIR / f\"{input_name}_chinese.mp4\")\n\n    progress(0.05, desc=\"📹 检查视频...\")\n    \n    try:\n        from video import get_video_info, extract_audio, replace_audio\n        from transcribe import transcribe\n        from translate import translate_segments, load_glossary\n        from tts import synthesize_segments\n        \n        # Step 0: Get video info\n        info = get_video_info(video_file)\n        duration = info.get('duration', 0) if info else 0\n        \n        progress(0.1, desc=f\"📹 视频时长 {duration:.0f}秒，开始处理...\")\n        \n        # Step 1: Extract audio\n        progress(0.15, desc=\"🔊 提取音频...\")\n        temp_dir = OUTPUT_DIR / 'temp'\n        temp_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=True)\n        audio_wav = str(temp_dir / 'original_audio.wav')\n        if not extract_audio(video_file, audio_wav):\n            return None, \"❌ 音频提取失败\"\n        progress(0.25, desc=\"✅ 音频提取完成\")\n        \n        # Step 2: Transcribe\n        progress(0.3, desc=\"🗣️ 转录英文语音中...\")\n        full_text, segments = transcribe(audio_wav, model_size=whisper_model, language='en')\n        if not full_text:\n            return None, \"❌ 转录失败\"\n        progress(0.5, desc=f\"✅ 转录完成 ({len(segments)} 段)\")\n        \n        # Step 3: Translate\n        progress(0.55, desc=\"🌐 翻译为中文...\")\n        load_glossary()\n        segments_with_translation = translate_segments(segments, from_lang='en', to_lang='zh')\n        translated_count = len([s for s in segments_with_translation if s.get('text_zh')])\n        progress(0.75, desc=f\"✅ 翻译完成 ({translated_count} 段)\")\n        \n        # Step 4: TTS\n        progress(0.8, desc=\"🔉 合成中文语音...\")\n        chinese_segments_dir = temp_dir / 'segments'\n        wav_files = synthesize_segments(segments_with_translation, chinese_segments_dir, voice=tts_voice)\n        if not wav_files:\n            return None, \"❌ 语音合成失败\"\n        progress(0.9, desc=f\"✅ 合成完成 ({len(wav_files)} 段)\")\n        \n        # Step 5: Merge and replace audio\n        progress(0.92, desc=\"🎵 合并音频...\")\n        from tts import synthesize_speech  # for concat\n        # Concatenate WAV files\n        chinese_audio = str(temp_dir / 'chinese_audio.wav')\n        concat_audio_segments(wav_files, chinese_audio)\n        \n        progress(0.95, desc=\"🎬 合成视频...\")\n        if not replace_audio(video_file, chinese_audio, output_path):\n            return None, \"❌ 视频合成失败\"\n        \n        progress(1.0, desc=\"✅ 完成！\")\n        \n        if os.path.exists(output_path):\n            file_size = os.path.getsize(output_path) / 1024 / 1024\n            return output_path, f\"✅ 处理完成！\\n输出: {Path(output_path).name}\\n大小: {file_size:.1f} MB\\n转录: {len(segments)} 段\\n翻译: {translated_count} 段\"\n        else:\n            return None, \"❌ 输出文件未生成\"\n\n    except Exception as e:\n        import traceback\n        traceback.print_exc()\n        return None, f\"❌ 错误: {str(e)}\"\n\n\ndef concat_audio_segments(wav_files, output_path):\n    \"\"\"Concatenate WAV files using ffmpeg.\"\"\"\n    import subprocess\n    list_file = Path(output_path).parent / 'concat_list.txt'\n    with open(list_file, 'w') as f:\n        for wav in wav_files:\n            f.write(f\"file '{wav}'\\n\")\n    cmd = ['ffmpeg', '-f', 'concat', '-safe', '0', '-i', str(list_file), \n           '-acodec', 'pcm_s16le', '-y', output_path]\n    subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True)"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":588,"output":2254,"cacheRead":204928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":207770,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773565031052}}
