{"type":"message","id":"f673be0c","parentId":"e88f226b","timestamp":"2026-03-15T09:15:42.294Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the bug! The `edge_tts.Communicate` expects `rate` as a string like `\"+10%\"`, not an integer. I passed `rate=rate` where `rate` was an integer. Let me fix this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"找到 bug！`edge_tts.Communicate` 的 `rate` 参数必须是字符串格式 `\"+10%\"`，我传了整数。修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"d797224f-bae3-4fb2-bdef-1342e45c5dcb","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/xzy0626/.openclaw/workspace/VoxBridge/src/tts.py","old_string":"async def _synthesize_with_rate(text, voice, rate, path):\n        ssml = build_ssml(text, voice, rate=rate)\n        communicate = edge_tts.Communicate(text, voice, rate=rate)\n        await communicate.save(path)","new_string":"async def _synthesize_with_rate(text, voice, rate, path):\n        rate_str = f\"{rate:+d}%\" if rate != 0 else \"+0%\"\n        communicate = edge_tts.Communicate(text, voice, rate=rate_str)\n        await communicate.save(path)"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":887,"output":294,"cacheRead":217664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":218845,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773566133441}}
