{"type":"message","id":"4897a5d2","parentId":"ad05aeba","timestamp":"2026-03-15T09:38:28.336Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking two things:\n1. Why am I being rate-limited by academic websites - is there a missing skill/tool they can help with?\n2. Are there newer/stronger algorithms or techniques available?\n\nFor the first question:\n- The rate limiting is because I'm using `web_fetch` which makes HTTP requests without proper headers/API keys\n- Solutions:\n  - Use a Brave Search API key (for web_search)\n  - Use Semantic Scholar API with a key\n  - Use Google Scholar through browser automation\n  - Add proper User-Agent headers to requests\n\nFor the second question:\n- I should mention some more recent techniques I know about from my training data\n- Things like: Wav2Lip, VideoReTalking, SadTalker for lip sync\n\n\n- For audio sync specifically: DTW (Dynamic Time Warping), neural audio codecs\n- For TTS naturalness: VALL-E XT, CosyVoice, Fish-Speech, ChatTTS\n\nLet me give a practical answer that addresses both the immediate rate-limiting issue and explores what newer approaches are available.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🔍 关于限流的问题\n\n不是缺少技能，是**没有 API key** 导致的：\n\n| 服务 | 限流原因 | 解决方案 |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| arXiv | 无 key，请求太频繁 | 申请 API key（免费）或加请求间隔 |\n| Semantic Scholar | 同上 | 申请 API key（免费） |\n| Brave Search | 缺少 `BRAVE_API_KEY` | `openclaw configure --section web` 配置 |\n\n**你能帮我的：**\n1. 申请 [Semantic Scholar API key](https://www.semanticscholar.org/product/api)（免费，瞬间批准）\n2. 或配置 Brave Search API key（`openclaw configure --section web`）\n\n有了 key 后我可以正常搜索学术论文。\n\n---\n\n## 🔬 更新更强的算法/技术（基于我的知识库）\n\n### 音画同步类\n\n| 技术/论文 | 年份 | 核心思路 | 可用性 |\n|-----------|------|---------|--------|\n| **Dynamic Time Warping (DTW)** | 经典 | 动态规划对齐两段音频的时间序列 | ✅ `python-dtw` 库直接可用 |\n| **Monotonic Alignment Search (MAS)** | 2023-24 | VITS/Tortoise-TTS 中的对齐算法 | 🟡 需要实现 |\n| **Wav2Vec2 Alignment** | 2024 | 用 wav2vec2 提取特征做 forced alignment | ✅ `transformers` 库 |\n| **Montreal Forced Aligner** | 持续更新 | 音素级精确对齐（Kaldi 后端） | 🟡 需安装，~2GB |\n\n### TTS 自然度类\n\n| 技术 | 年份 | 特点 | CPU 可用？ |\n|------|------|------|-----------|\n| **ChatTTS** | 2024 | 超自然对话 TTS，支持笑声/停顿 | ✅ 有 CPU 版 |\n| **CosyVoice** (阿里) | 2024 | 多语言、少样本克隆、情感控制 | 🟡 需 GPU |\n| **Fish-Speech** | 2024 | 开源高质量，支持零样本 | 🟡 较重 |\n| **edge-tts prosody** | 2024 | SSML `<mstts:express-as>` 情感标签 | ✅ 已在用 |\n\n### 视频配音整体方案\n\n| 项目 | 年份 | 能力 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **VideoLingo** | 2024 | 完整 pipeline：字幕+配音+对口型 |\n| **KrillinAI** | 2024 | 类似 VoxBridge，但功能更全 |\n| **GPT-SoVITS** | 2024 | 声音克隆 + TTS |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 我建议立即做的优化\n\n**基于现有 edge-tts，不换 TTS 引擎：**\n\n1. **Crossfade 拼接**（SmoothDub 论文）- 消除片段间的爆音\n2. **翻译长度控制**（VideoDubber 论文）- 翻译时控制字数接近原文\n3. **SSML 情感标签** - edge-tts 支持 `<mstts:express-as style=\"newscast\">`\n4. **Dynamic Time Warping** - 比 atempo 更精确的对齐\n\n**如果想大幅提升 TTS 质量：**\n5. **ChatTTS** - 超自然对话级 TTS，专门优化了\"人味\"\n\n---\n\n要我先实现哪几个？还是你先帮我配个 API key 方便我查论文？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":2095,"output":1347,"cacheRead":226688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":230130,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773567196750}}
