{"type":"message","id":"5fb32d6b","parentId":"fc889ba1","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:25:24.249Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `openclaw configure --section web` command opens an interactive TUI, which I can't use. Let me check if there's a way to set the Brave API key via command line or environment variable.Actually, I should tell the user that I don't see any new academic API configuration. The web_search tool still needs a Brave API key. The user said WorkBuddy configured something, but I don't see it.Maybe it's configured through an environment variable or a different mechanism. Let me check if there's a .env file or if the API key is set elsewhere.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"没有发现新增的学术 API 配置。让我确认一下当前状态：\n\n---\n\n## 📋 当前检查结果\n\n| 工具/服务 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|-----------|------|------|\n| `web_search` (Brave) | ❌ 缺少 `BRAVE_API_KEY` | 需要配置 |\n| Semantic Scholar API | ❌ 未配置 | 需要 API key |\n| arXiv API | ⚠️ 限流 | 无 key，需加间隔 |\n| MCP servers | ❌ 无新增 | - |\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 需要你帮忙做的\n\n**方案 A：配置 Brave Search API（推荐）**\n```bash\nopenclaw configure --section web\n```\n然后填入 Brave Search API key（免费申请：https://brave.com/search/api/）\n\n**方案 B：直接设置环境变量**\n```bash\n# 在 VM 终端执行\nexport BRAVE_API_KEY=\"你的key\"\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n**方案 C：配置 Semantic Scholar API**\n在 `openclaw.json` 里添加：\n```json\n{\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"semanticScholar\": {\n      \"apiKey\": \"你的key\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 如果暂时没有 API key\n\n我可以用 **web_fetch** 抓取具体论文页面（已知 URL），手动查找。只是搜索功能受限。\n\n你希望：\n1. **现在配置 API key** → 我等你配好\n2. **先跳过搜索，继续优化代码** → 我实现 crossfade + 长度控制\n3. **你帮我找几篇论文链接** → 我直接抓取阅读\n\n选哪个？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":891,"output":636,"cacheRead":230784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":232311,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773570303973}}
