{"type":"message","id":"8832abb4","parentId":"cd0ca694","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:35:19.558Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The academic search is working well. I found several highly relevant papers:\n\n1. **FCConDubber** (2025, ICASSP) - Fine And Coarse Grained Prosody Alignment for Expressive Video Dubbing via Contrastive Audio-Motion Pretraining\n2. **Integrating Dynamics and Timing Alignment** (2025) - Natural Multilingual Video Dubbing\n3. **Gen AI driven multilingual audio dubbing** (2025) - Cross-language video platforms\n4. **Automating Multilingual Video Dubbing** (2024) - Deep learning and audio synthesis\n\n\n5. **VALL-E** (2023) - Neural Codec Language Models are Zero-Shot TTS\n6. **NaturalSpeech 2** (2023) - Latent Diffusion Models for Speech\n7. **Word-level Text Markup for Prosody Control** (2024, Interspeech)\n8. **Style and Prosody control for Zero-shot Speech Synthesis** (2025, SSW)\n\nI'm also seeing several other relevant papers on prosody control and zero-shot synthesis that could be useful for refining the approach.\n\nThe most promising immediate techniques I can implement are prosody markup at the word level, time stretching which I've already started on, contrastive alignment similar to what FCConDubber uses, emotion control from edge-tts, and crossfade transitions based on SmoothDub. Now I want to dig into the most practical papers to extract concrete implementation details.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了很多相关论文！让我深入阅读最相关的几篇："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"4b147855-5faf-4d0c-9cba-eb053b85b5c6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 /home/xzy0626/.openclaw/scripts/academic_search.py --doi \"10.1109/icassp49660.2025.10887957\"","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"e0311429-b500-4b89-a0db-a36b45d1ce82","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 /home/xzy0626/.openclaw/scripts/academic_search.py --doi \"10.21437/interspeech.2024-715\"","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"c093e5f2-ce2f-4f4b-aa8f-b6b9a6e2a53e","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2301.02111","maxChars":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":4433,"output":873,"cacheRead":236032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":241338,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773570894592}}
